'''scooter'''
# a [[small]] two-wheeled [[motorized]] [[vehicle]] with a [[step-thru]] [[frame]] : [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scooter_%28motorcycle%29 MOTOR SCOOTER]
# a [[motorcycle]] with a [[step-thru]] [[frame]] : [[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scooter_%28motorcycle%29 MAXI SCOOTER]
