# a [[motorized]] chair with three or four wheels that [[steers]] using handlebars designed for people with [[limited]] [[mobility]] : [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mobility_scooter MOBILITY SCOOTER]
# a [[corruption]] of [[Scoter]], a large black diving [[duck]] of the northern hemisphere

